{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji17","name":"毛泽东全集第17卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/maoquanji17.pdf"],"article":{"title":"致胡宗南电","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"致胡宗南电"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1942年5月19日）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"据报贵部正在积极动员进攻边区，采取袭击办法，一举夺取延安，此种军事行动归陶峙岳指挥，总兵力为五个军等语。事属骇人听闻，大敌当前，岂堪有此，敢电奉询，即祈示复。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[1]这是毛泽东为朱德起草的致胡宗南电的主要内容。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1942,"month":5,"day":19}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":67,"page_end":67},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}